# SNMP configuration in Zabbix\n# Add SNMP device via Zabbix frontend and configure SNMP community string and OIDs\n\n# JMX configuration in Zabbix\n# Add JMX interface to your host in Zabbix and set up the Zabbix Java Gateway\n\n# TIBCO Hawk integration\n# Create a custom script to fetch TIBCO Hawk metrics and send them to Zabbix using zabbix_sender\n# Example script (hawk_metrics.sh):\n#!/bin/bash\n# Fetch metrics from TIBCO Hawk and send to Zabbix\nmetrics=$(hawk_command_to_fetch_metrics)  # Replace with actual command\nzabbix_sender -z <ZABBIX_SERVER> -s <HOST_NAME> -k <METRIC_KEY> -o "$metrics"